content:
"Hello, I expected to get added to the Vote Team channels after doing a shadow chat captain shift and filling out the debriefing form. I am also scheduled for the Discord mod info call tonight. (I coulnd't find a way to add a ? to the general support channel) Thanks in advance for any info, others said they got added right away. I don't see a dm or the channels. I'll go check my spam folders to see if new address is being held..."
<@682129533041901620>

Hi <@682129533041901620> I'll answer this here, since first step is to help you find the DMs, then we can move over there. Look at the top left of your screen, there is a game-player icon (discord logo) tap on that and it will open the direct message panel. you will see a red dot because I have sent you a friend request. click that and you can message me from there. I will also be in the Zoom chat during the discord training later today, so you can connect with me there if we don't meet sooner.

<@477560366432256000> Hi Jack, I got a message from Scale to Win with the following: ‚ÄúPermission Required
You haven't been added as an admin to this organization. Another admin will need to add you before you can access the dialer. ‚Äú Please advise.
Not sure why you tagged me into this.
<@&1242252399284977714> Person needs help with dialer. Sorry for tagging all of us.
Hi LisaA, what is the link that you are using?
Democrat.scaletowin.com/
Are you in the Zoom phone bank now?
No I attended Saturday
LisaA, did you get the link from the Zoom phone bank session on Saturday?
I was given the link after the call.
Ok.  Thanks.  The link is not working for me either.  Let me keep researching.
Thank you!
We have another call moderator coming on in a few minutes.  I've tagged him here to assist as well.  <@112080668296564736>
Thanks much!
Hi Lisa, the dialer changes every shift. When you are in the zoom chat, the new dialer link will be posted for you to use for that session!
Let me know if that makes sense or if you have any other questions!
My Zoom training was Saturday.  Should I join another zoom to get this working?  I have already setup my Discord account.
Nope, just anytime you sign up to phone bank you'll join the zoom for that session and you will get the dialer link for that session. You don't need an account for that website!
Ah, gotcha!  I‚Äôll try now.
